approve(uint256,uint256).details: Approves another EIN to transfer the given token ID The zero EIN indicates there is no approved EIN. There can only be one approved EIN per token at a given time. Can only be called by the token owner or an approved operator.

params.to: uint256 to be approved for the given token ID
params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to be approved

params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to be approved
